'''''Sacrifice of the Widow''''' is the first book in [[The Lady Penitent]] trilogy by [[Lisa Smedman]].

{{quote|''[[Halisstra Melarn]], convert to the cause of the goddess [[Eilistraee]], was sent to the deepest depths of the [[Outer Planes]] to kill the [[Lolth|demon goddess]] she once worshiped, but instead was transformed into a hideous creature bent to the vengeful will of her former mistress. For the Queen of the [[Demonweb Pits]] not only survived her [[Silence of Lolth|Silence]] but evolved into something greater than she was before—something that no longer needs to share the domain she calls her own.''

''Could it be that the [[War of the Spider Queen]] has just begun?''}}
